Taking viewers back to the early days of the Daphne 
(Kate Melton), Velma (Hayley Kiyoko), Fred (Robbie 
Amell) and Shaggy (Nick Palatas) alliance, this Brian 
Levant-directed prequel tells the story of how the 
teenage sleuths solved their first case to restore 
their own good names. Suspended from Coolsville High, 
the kids -- along with Shaggy's pup, Scooby-Doo --are 
determined to prove they aren't the ones who staged 
a spooky joke.

Starring: Robbie Amell, Nick Palatas

Director: Brian Levant
